    • createRequest

      public void createRequest​(boolean saveRespond, java.lang.String nameOutput, boolean headerRespond, boolean followRedirect) throws java.io.IOException
      In this method we create a new HttpUrlConnection and also split the body and header and set them in the right place (also method and url) and shoe the respond of request
      Parameters:
      saveRespond - : boolean that tell us we want to save a respond or not
      nameOutput - :if we want to save a respond whats the name
      headerRespond - boolean that tell us we want to show a headerFields or not
      followRedirect - boolean that tell us if re url is redirect chose the right url
      Throws:
      java.io.IOException
